verbose_text: Thus, the small upregulation of Wnt activity still induced by butyrate in the presence of DN-Tcf4 expression (1.9-fold) is an order of magnitude less (P < 0.001) than that induced by butyrate in the absence of DN-Tcf4 (19.3-fold) (compare NaB / Ctl to DoxyNaB / Doxy in Figure XREF_FIG B).
evidence: induced by butyrate in the absence of DN-Tcf4
